{
  "texts": [
    "The task assigned to the English-language students was relatively generic, lacking a clear connection to subject-specific skills or specialized content.",
    "As a result, participants in the interviews did not comment on whether the AI feedback improved their",
    "writing skills.",
    "Instead, they primarily focused on how the feedback helped them generate new arguments or ideas.",
    "This observation aligns with concerns raised by Knoth et al. (2024), who highlight the limitations of AI in analytical tasks, suggesting it performs better in generating content than in providing deeper critical or analytical insights."
  ]
}